goals.active: Win the hyleks' Tournament of the Sun God.
goals.complete: With Ikniu's help, I won the Tournament of the Sun God. The hylek were willing to listen to a tournament champion, and I convinced Chief Quecuan that we must defend the village from the undead, not offer sacrifices to them. High Priestess Ecolotl disagreed and stormed off, but the rest of the hylek joined in our plans to fortify and defend the village.
